{DIALOGUE}: And when the band plays "Hail to the Chief," ohh, they point the cannon at you all.
{DIALOGUE}: It ain't me.
{DIALOGUE}: It ain't me.
{DIALOGUE}: I ain't no Senator's son, no.
{DIALOGUE}: It ain't me.
{DIALOGUE}: It ain't me..."
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Bubba and Forrest jump out of the helicopter with their gear/ They walk and look around oddly.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: FORREST (V.O.)
{DIALOGUE}: Now, they told us that Vietnam was gonna be very different from the United Sates of America.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The soldier places a case of beer on a large stack of cases.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He takes two beers out and walks away.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: In the background, soldiers are barbecuing steaks and drinking beer.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: FORREST (V.O.)
{DIALOGUE}: Except for all the beer cans and the barbecue, it was.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BUBBA
{DIALOGUE}: Y'know, I bet there's shrimp all in these waters.
{DIALOGUE}: They tell me these Vietnams is good shrimp.
{DIALOGUE}: You know, after we win this war, and we take over everything we can get American shrimpers to come on here and shrimp these waters.
{DIALOGUE}: We'll just shrimp all the time, man.
{DIALOGUE}: So much shrimp, why, you wouldn't believe it.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Lieutenant DAN TAYLOR steps out of a tent.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Shirtless, he holds a roll of toilet paper in his hand.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LT. DAN
{DIALOGUE}: You must be my F.N.G.'s.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BUBBA AND FORREST
{DIALOGUE}: Morning', sir!
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LT. DAN
{DIALOGUE}: Ho!
{DIALOGUE}: Get your hands down.
{DIALOGUE}: Do not salute me.
{DIALOGUE}: There are goddamned snipers all around this area who would love to grease an officer.
{DIALOGUE}: I'm Lieutenant Dan Taylor.
{DIALOGUE}: Welcome to Fourth Platoon.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Lt. Dan looks at Bubba.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LT. DAN
{DIALOGUE}: What's wrong with your lips?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BUBBA
{DIALOGUE}: I was born with big gums, sir.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LT. DAN
{DIALOGUE}: Yeah, well, you better tuck that in.
{DIALOGUE}: Gonna get that caught on a trip wire.
{DIALOGUE}: Where you boys from in the world?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BUBBA & FORREST
{DIALOGUE}: Alabama, sir!
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LT. DAN
{DIALOGUE}: You twins?
