{DIALOGUE}: "There's something happenin' here.
{DIALOGUE}: What it is ain't exactly clear.
{DIALOGUE}: There's a man with a gun over there, telling' me I got to beware."
{CHARACTER_NAME}: FORREST (V.O.)
{DIALOGUE}: This one day, we was out walking, like always, and then, just like that, somebody turned off the rain and the sun come out.
