{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Forrest rolls over and pulls his pack off Lt. Dan lies next to Forrest.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LT. DAN
{DIALOGUE}: Get that pig up here, goddammit!
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BUBBA
{DIALOGUE}: Forrest, you okay?
