{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Lt. Dan shouts into the radio.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Forrest begins firing his weapon into the jungle.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LT. DAN
{DIALOGUE}: ...Strongarm, please be advised...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Two soldiers pull a wounded soldier into the jungle.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BUBBA
{DIALOGUE}: Medic, we got a man down!
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LT. DAN
{DIALOGUE}: Strongarm, this is Leg Lima 6, over!
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LT. DAN
{DIALOGUE}: Roger, Strongarm, be advised we have incoming from the treeline at point blue plus two.
{DIALOGUE}: A.K's and rockets...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The machine gunner fires into the treeline.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Another soldier helps him with the ammunition.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The machine gun jams.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SOLDIER WITH BIG MACHINE GUN
{DIALOGUE}: Misfire!
{DIALOGUE}: Misfire!
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LT. DAN
{DIALOGUE}: Goddammit, Mac!
{DIALOGUE}: Get that pig unfucked and get it in the treeline!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A rocket explodes on the machine gunner and the other soldier, killing them.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Forrest looks down and covers his head as rockets explodes all around him.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LT. DAN
{META_DATA}: (into radio)
{DIALOGUE}: Ah, Jesus!
{DIALOGUE}: My unit is down hard and hurting!
{DIALOGUE}: 6 pulling back to the blue line, Leg Lima 6 out!
{DIALOGUE}: Pull back!
{DIALOGUE}: Pull back!
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BUBBA
{DIALOGUE}: Forrest!
{DIALOGUE}: Run!
{DIALOGUE}: Run, Forrest!
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LT. DAN
{DIALOGUE}: Pull back!
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BUBBA
{DIALOGUE}: Forrest!
{DIALOGUE}: Run!
{DIALOGUE}: Run, Forrest!
{DIALOGUE}: Run!
{DIALOGUE}: Run!
