{DIALOGUE}: Pull back!
{DIALOGUE}: Let's go!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Lt. Dan gets up and grabs Forrest by the collar.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LT. DAN
{DIALOGUE}: Run, goddammit, run!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The platoon gets up and runs toward the cover of the jungle.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Rockets explode all around the field.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Forrest runs into the jungle.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The soldiers run through the jungle as bullets explode all around.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A soldier is blown up by a rocket.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A soldier runs through the jungle.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Forrest runs past the soldier.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SOLDIER
{DIALOGUE}: Medic!
{DIALOGUE}: Medic!
{DIALOGUE}: Jesus, can I get a medic?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: FORREST (V.O.)
{DIALOGUE}: I ran and ran, just like Jenny told me to.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Rockets explode in the jungle as Forrest runs out toward a clearing.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: FORREST (V.O.)
