{DIALOGUE}: Everybody gets a second chance.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: FORREST (V.O.)
{DIALOGUE}: It's funny, but in the middle of all that fun, I began to think about Jenny.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: DICK CLARK
{META_DATA}: (on television)
{DIALOGUE}: ...getting wild out there.
{DIALOGUE}: It's beginning to...
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. APARTMENT/L.A. - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The New Year's Eve celebration over the T.V.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: DICK CLARK
