{DIALOGUE}: "Should auld acquaintance be forgot and never brought to mind...
{CHARACTER_NAME}: FORREST
{DIALOGUE}: Happy New Year, Lieutenant Dan!
{CHARACTER_NAME}: PATRONS
{META_DATA}: (sing)
{DIALOGUE}: Should auld acquaintance be forgot and days of auld lang syne."
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. LT. DAN'S HOTEL ROOM - LATER
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Carla removes her top and sits on top of Dan in his wheelchair.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They kiss and play around.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Forrest sits in a chair.
