{DIALOGUE}: Oh, you look good, Forrest.
{DIALOGUE}: You look real good.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: FORREST (V.O.)
{DIALOGUE}: That Momma, she sure was right.
{DIALOGUE}: It's funny how things work out.
