{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He smiles, surprised.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: FORREST
{DIALOGUE}: Hi!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Forrest leaps off of his moving boat and into the water.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The boat continues as Forrest clumsily swims.
