{CHARACTER_NAME}: FORREST
{DIALOGUE}: Okay.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LT. DAN
{DIALOGUE}: Gump, what are you doing?
{DIALOGUE}: Take a left!
{DIALOGUE}: Left!
{DIALOGUE}: That's where we're gonna find those shrimp, my boy!
{DIALOGUE}: That's where we'll find 'em.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Forrest empties the net.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Their "catch" is debris that falls to the deck.
