{DIALOGUE}: Okay, so I was wrong.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: FORREST
{DIALOGUE}: Well, how we gonna find them?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LT. DAN
{DIALOGUE}: Well, maybe you should just pray for shrimp.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. SMALL CHURCH - DAY
