{DIALOGUE}: Yes, sir.
{DIALOGUE}: We've got more money than Davy Crocket.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: MAN
{DIALOGUE}: Boy, I've heard some whoppers in my time, but that tops them all.
{DIALOGUE}: We was sitting next to a millionaire!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The man laughs as he walks away.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ELDERLY WOMAN
{DIALOGUE}: Well, I thought it was a very lovely story.
{DIALOGUE}: And you tell it so well.
{DIALOGUE}: With such enthusiasm.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: FORREST
{DIALOGUE}: Would you like to see what Lieutenant Dan looks like?
